import React from 'react'
import { Container } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { BreadCrumb } from '../components/BreadCrumb/BreadCrumb.comp'

export const Ticket = () => {
  return (
   <Container>
    <Rol>
        <Col>
        <BreadCrumb page={"Ticket"}></BreadCrumb>
        </Col>
    </Rol>
   </Container>
  )
}
